    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a major project. The exterior shows significant wear with extensive rust on the rocker panels and a large dent in the rear passenger door. Mechanically, the transmission is beginning to slip between second and third gear, and there is a persistent oil leak that requires frequent topping off. The interior has seen heavy use, with several tears in the upholstery and a non-functioning air conditioning system. While the car does start and drive, it will need immediate repairs to be considered reliable for daily use.",
