    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this investment-grade vehicle, preserved in concours-level condition. This specimen exhibits flawless paintwork, a pristine interior entirely free of wear, and a mechanical profile that mirrors its original factory specifications. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Discerning enthusiasts will appreciate the uncompromising integrity and exceptional provenance of this rare find.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
