    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute gem of a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garage-kept and pampered since day one, showing no signs of wear on its flawless, ceramic-coated exterior. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, documented service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this is a rare find for a discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. Included with the sale are all original keys, owner's manuals, and a custom-fit breathable car cover.",
      "price": 47500.0,
