      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2017 BMW M2, a masterclass in longitudinal dynamics and chassis balance. This F87-generation example features the N55 3.0L inline-six equipped with TwinPower Turbo technology, delivering a flat torque curve and immediate throttle response. Power is delivered to the rear wheels through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and an electronically controlled Active M Differential for optimal corner-exit traction. The vehicle retains its factory-spec suspension geometry, ensuring precise turn-in and high lateral G-loading capability. Meticulously preserved with flawless paint depth and an interior devoid of bolster wear, this specimen reflects rigorous mechanical upkeep and zero track-use fatigue. A turn-key acquisition for the driver who demands mechanical transparency and structural integrity.",
